Name: Minimum time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and any subsequent \due in\ notification activity (e.g., SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days)
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days'

Name: Average time from Plagiarism Originality Report Completed to SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and SW-Awaiting AE Assignment
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-Checklist Completed after the execution of Plagiarism Originality Report Completed
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Time from Plagiarism Originality Report Completed to SW-Initial Reviewer Selection in variants that include both activities
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Elapsed time between Manuscript Export Succeeded and Plagiarism Originality Report Completed compared to the elapsed time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Average waiting time to SW-Checklist Completed after Plagiarism Originality Report Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total resolution time of Plagiarism Originality Report Completed in cases leading to SW-EIC Reject versus cases leading to SW-EIC Accept
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Time of Plagiarism Originality Report Completed in variants involving Plagiarism Percent Match Threshold Exceeded versus variants without it
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and the end of case where activity 'Plagiarism Percent Match Threshold Exceeded occurs

Name: Minimum time from Plagiarism Originality Report Completed to SW-AE Assign Reviewers in high-performance variants (performance < median variant duration)
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Average time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and the next reviewer-related activity (e.g., SW-Initial Reviewer Selection or SW-AE Assign Reviewers)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Total time it takes SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to be reached after Plagiarism Originality Report Completed in revised manuscript tracks versus original submission tracks
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Cycle Time of Plagiarism Originality Report Completed measured from Manuscript Export Succeeded to SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Time from Plagiarism Originality Report Completed to SW-Reviewer Agreed in variants where reviewer assignment eventually succeeds
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Minimum time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and any subsequent due in notification activity (e.g., SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days)
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days'
